<p>BORROWER MERCANTILE BANCORP INC</p>
<p>AMT $200 MILLION   COUPON 7.30 PCT    MATURITY 6/15/2007</p>
<p>TYPE SUB NOTES     ISS PRICE 100.00   FIRST PAY DATE 12/15/97</p>
